islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小林出嘅呢支，一般萬寧賣五十零，噴落背脊涼浸浸，好似安美露啲薄荷咁，好正<br />\n佢就聲稱自己keep到幾粒鐘，但我覺得兩粒鐘就極限，要再噴<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/225956_b53cd30bdd5c69d2d2ebd2e63af8cd99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F225956_b53cd30bdd5c69d2d2ebd2e63af8cd99.jpg&h=1d64ab3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用落有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有諗緊買</blockquote><br />\n幾有用<br />\n因為裝full suit 返工，出門口至追到公司有d會無冷氣 特別係搭lift，會出汗<br />\n出門口之前噴底衫，夠涼到返公司就有冷氣，至少放工之前都唔會出汗"},{"pid":"d1a39b3ec9f25a438a2156e77fbbed0dff4f0775","tid":392494,"uid":1314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:52:36.000Z","msg":"好多時啲老豆都係呻下啫 我覺得唔使搞咁多野<br />\n煲啲消暑湯水 綠豆水俾佢開工飲<br />\n講真唔係坐寫字樓嘅工 夏天邊份唔熱<br />\n買個噴壺水樽俾佢都好舒服<br />\n夜晚返黎幫佢洗衫囉 等佢係屋企真正休息下"},{"pid":"b4142c06a23ad313cb1fd973a72fa08a66864c1e","tid":392494,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小林出嘅呢支，一般萬寧賣五十零，噴落背脊涼浸浸，好似安美露啲薄荷咁，好正<br />\n佢就聲稱自己keep到幾粒鐘，但我覺得兩粒鐘就極限，要再噴<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/225956_b53cd30bdd5c69d2d2ebd2e63af8cd99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F225956_b53cd30bdd5c69d2d2ebd2e63af8cd99.jpg&h=1d64ab3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用落有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有諗緊買</blockquote><br />\n好正，好似你食完薄菏糖飲水咁</blockquote><br />\n但係小心 有啲出汗位噴完會好那，之前係台灣買過 所以要擦乾啲汗先好噴</blockquote><br />\n唔可以直噴皮膚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要噴衫"},{"pid":"2ff62549d9adf062350653729f5adf54a9471ecb","tid":392494,"uid":113966,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"我老豆都做地盤 熱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以成日都好想落雨等老豆唔洗番工係屋企休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主可以去優品360買冰手「就」<br />\n同埋買把風扇仔 （佢帶兩部番工）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c80634207d01e168e3afc4a065b534511dac95","tid":392494,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"貼小林退熱貼"},{"pid":"384e3d780f0067c3679dd07f6b630ef2775b5cd8","tid":392494,"uid":113966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老豆都做地盤 熱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以成日都好想落雨等老豆唔洗番工係屋企休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主可以去優品360買冰手「就」<br />\n同埋買把風扇仔 （佢帶兩部番工）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有煲冬瓜水消暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9670978db49d8077f2cda9e19fa47e8f5b070735","tid":392494,"uid":3067,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱先發現到樣正野，降溫噴霧，噴落去會好涼</blockquote><br />\n唔好撚搞呢d野 <br />\n你人體高溫 外面又熱<br />\n個人本身就 不斷郁動 <br />\n你外來有野 突然噴落黎 降溫 <br />\n係好易暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"h