 />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我買二代USB插淨風扇，電用小米尿袋10000mah放腰包，有三種強度，多數開中間，6個鐘左右應該冇問題，有時做室內冇冷氣只係焗開最細，其他同事個個都臭晒，我仲係乾爽</blockquote><br />\n好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks巴打"},{"pid":"41ed7316dfcf22c659daa1243e7d81bc3a8a2ead","tid":392494,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"Samsung 好似出過一件背心<br />\n件背心會傳熱去背脊然後有把抽氣扇抽走個熱力"},{"pid":"8e990cbbacae7ed64df706a78e6ccec5b29ed4e4","tid":392494,"uid":28865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"columbia 好似出過件tee 有水份 eg 汗 整濕左件三會變凍 個陣沙灘有人promote 我試過覺得幾work 件三又唔厚，不過就唔知幾錢喇，你預可能都要五百一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e26a289c70897a169ad2aaedc81dab2c1de2d7","tid":392494,"uid":11651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:03:52.000Z","msg":"除左買部保路華比佢，其他野都無用<br />\n利申： 做地盤"},{"pid":"196c5aab1fcb3028d0ade5752bbcb67f53b8ad4c","tid":392494,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\nFor我自己用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e917fda7ce4914018104fdc96839d9b77b1053","tid":392494,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"冰墊 退熱貼？"},{"pid":"38ab1abc28d3f514d110ea525f7a3dfac0a755e3","tid":392494,"uid":15800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"啲冰爽濕紙巾記得唔好長敷，好多人有出粒粒既現象<br />\n<br />\n乖仔，幫推"},{"pid":"c318f9129bf4d0d25b015ce8471f058d8a52acba","tid":392494,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"做泥水唔會著衫嫁<br />\n通常一對膠手套<br />\n短打<br />\n水鞋仔"},{"pid":"82a4567e030f557851893ca1ca7305cdc21b631d","tid":392494,"uid":14838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"買件平價風褸，再去街市搵人幫你車風扇上去！"},{"pid":"9dfb988a1cd3