,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2282dd2234070a410fd00dfd40424eff47563fe0","tid":392494,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呻下好熱好哂你估真係好熱好哂咩？<br />\n做左幾廿年地盤會唔慣？<br />\n你估佢唔會去抖咩？<br />\n係咪你冇比家用咋</blockquote><br />\n幾廿年前平均溫度同呢幾年比<br />\n識人做天面，都話呢幾年曬住做皮膚係刺痛，之前唔會"},{"pid":"350d31402c86d64ecf3fc5cd1903222bb13c840d","tid":392494,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"搵份好工養返佢啦戇鳩手"},{"pid":"5c39db0fa5085b61e65cc2ebe8da69139e470ee7","tid":392494,"uid":53190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T03:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前我係某寶買左件叫冰鎮馬甲嘅野，可以試試<br />\n著上身幾涼爽，缺點係件野乾到一個地步嘅時候會好難頂<br />\n另外有見到一種衫，裡面有好多袋位比你塞啲冰種入去<br />\n不過睇落好累贅，所以冇買黎試</blockquote><br />\n果然冇失望，做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個應該我阿爸會用，因為濕水就得，風扇外套兩舊野有D麻煩<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lv0fx3yj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flv0fx3yj&h=90fae4ae&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好用 好易風濕"},{"pid":"6dbc7109237020f6136824c40268bb756f152f24","tid":392494,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31040c53ced368de584f893080717f5398d39a48","tid":392494,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"三防手機真有用？"},{"pid":"7fa73f63ebb181f47faa9b49734c2bf70eb2ab15","tid":392494,"uid":136355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前我係某寶買左件叫冰鎮馬甲嘅野，可以試試<br />\n著上身幾涼爽，缺點係件野乾到一個地步嘅時候會好難頂<br />\n另外有見到一種衫，裡面有好多袋位比你塞啲冰種入去<br />\n不過睇落好累贅，所以冇買黎試</blockquote><br />\n果然冇失望，做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個應該我阿爸會用，因為濕水就得，風扇外套兩舊野有D麻煩<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lv0fx3yj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flv0fx3yj&h=90fae4ae&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n千祈唔好，我以前就係咁搞到成日風濕背痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加水會好重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9329f7121a16017486a0d065b7bc0625aedaa578","tid":392494,"uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小林出嘅呢支，一般萬寧賣五十零，噴落背脊涼浸浸，好似安美露啲薄荷咁，好正<br />\n佢就聲稱自己keep到幾粒鐘，但我覺得兩粒鐘就極限，要再噴<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/225956_b53cd30bdd5c69d2d2ebd2e63af8cd99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F225956_b53cd30bdd5c69d2d2ebd2e63af8cd99.jpg&h=1d64ab3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我聽日買，唔該哂</blockquote><br />\n噴落件衫度好喇，之前直接噴喺身乸到仆街"},{"pid":"76d2affb77ac154884cac0b0b428d579057cd7f0","tid":392494,"uid":13283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"好多時只係呻吓熱想人關心吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：同老豆一齊父子檔做裝修<br />\n戶外嘅真係靠飲多啲水，戴頂草帽防曬，拎多兩三套衫褲毛巾返工，毛巾濕完水放喺草帽上面幫手散吓熱，做嘢做到咁上下，匿埋喺陰涼地方食返飛煙，最緊要唔好比人周到"},{"pid":"ba398531021c16c82fe628ce82063b23dd6622a4","tid":392494,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80b809c62c728beb1511d26d59d220302f88fdcb","tid":392494,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"gatsby 個隻濕紙巾<br />\n好涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f083cfbf412ba3c790c3ce01c7847109b00f80","tid":392494,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:50:50.000Z","msg":"要睇你老豆做咩地盤 同 咩 工種 如果係落石矢著下呢d風扇衫都ok 如果釘板扎鐵就著唔落啦 阻自己做野 加上 如果係做mtr既盤 要外加反光衣 根本唔會想再著任何野 最有效方法係。。孝順佢多d佢做野個時會諗起你"},{"pid":"00db3ff4eb80d31dcd26703608c58b6009316c18","tid":392494,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/09/130128_f63218df1e13a4b0538b17336fff4c70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F09%2F130128_f63218df1e13a4b0538b17336fff4c70.jpg&h=a43519cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n掛腰扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e78ef66740157ddce71491372fbc6f7a4cf03ab","tid":392494,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"買左了<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g50alc84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg50alc84&h=1dcd6f12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcc2eacd136da20e09249083641a61faeb4349a7","tid":392494,"uid":79424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"絲打有冇男朋友，我願意為外父扇涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31264e6dd638247b2fa7fc2052ed0919faaf44c1","tid":392494,"uid":79424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打有冇男朋友，我願意為外父扇涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌當我冇講過"},{"pid":"1b6455800e3887f719ddf2bbdb16f9b9f0c53d07","tid":392494,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絲打有冇男朋友，我願意為外父扇涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌當我冇講過</blockquote><br />\n做咩啫你"},{"pid":"3fa